Plans for 0.7.1/0.8.0
=====================

  Updated translations:
    [D] Polish (pl)


Plans after 0.7.0
=================

  * Text correction assistants
     - Common error correction
     - Capitalization correction
     - Line reformatting
     - Hearing impaired subtitle removal


Unscheduled
===========

  * Windows installer
